+## 2. 算法实现
+
+### 2.1 等额本息（Declining Balance – Equal Installments）
+
+#### 计算公式
+
+每期还款额（PMT）由以下公式确定：
+
+```
+PMT = P × [r(1+r)^n] / [(1+r)^n - 1]
+
+其中：
+  P  = 剩余本金（Outstanding Balance）
+  r  = 每期利率（Periodic Interest Rate）
+  n  = 剩余期数（Remaining Periods）
+```
+
+每期利息 = 剩余本金 × 每期利率
+每期本金 = PMT - 每期利息
+
+#### 代码实现位置
+
+1. **PMT 数学函数**：[FinanicalFunctions.pmt()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/FinanicalFunctions.java#L32-L55)
+   ```java
+   public static double pmt(final double interestRateFraction, final double numberOfPayments,
+           final double principal, final double futureValue, final boolean type) {
+       // c = (r / (1 - (1 + r)^-N)) * P
+       // 使用 double 计算，存在精度风险
+       if (interestRateFraction == 0) {
+           payment = -1 * (futureValue + principal) / numberOfPayments;
+       } else {
+           final double r1 = interestRateFraction + 1;
+           payment = (futureValue + principal * Math.pow(r1, numberOfPayments)) * interestRateFraction
+                   / ((type ? r1 : 1) * (1 - Math.pow(r1, numberOfPayments)));
+       }
+   }
+   ```
+
+2. **PMT 调用入口**：[LoanApplicationTerms.pmtForInstallment()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1004-L1018)
+   - 使用 `DaysInMonthType.DAYS_30` 和 `DaysInYearType.DAYS_365` 作为默认周期利率计算的基准
+   - 调用 `calculateTotalDueForEqualInstallmentRepaymentPeriod()` 获取 PMT 金额
+
+3. **每期本金计算**：[LoanApplicationTerms.calculatePrincipalDueForInstallment()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1710-L1717)
+   ```java
+   private Money calculatePrincipalDueForInstallment(final int periodNumber,
+           final Money totalDuePerInstallment, final Money periodInterest) {
+       Money principal = totalDuePerInstallment.minus(periodInterest);
+       if (isPrincipalGraceApplicableForThisPeriod(periodNumber)) {
+           principal = principal.zero();
+       }
+       return principal;
+   }
+   ```
+
+### 2.2 等额本金（Declining Principal – Equal Principal）
+
+#### 计算公式
+
+每期偿还本金固定，利息逐期递减：
+
+```
+每期本金 = 贷款本金 / 还款总期数
+每期利息 = 剩余本金 × 每期利率
+每期还款额 = 每期本金 + 每期利息
+```
+
+#### 代码实现位置
+
+[LoanApplicationTerms.calculateEqualPrincipalDueForInstallment()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1670-L1692)
+```java
+private Money calculateEqualPrincipalDueForInstallment(final MathContext mc, final int periodNumber) {
+    Money principal = this.principal;
+    if (this.fixedPrincipalAmount == null) {
+        final Integer numberOfPrincipalPaymentPeriods = calculateNumberOfRemainingPrincipalPaymentPeriods(
+            this.actualNumberOfRepayments, periodNumber);
+        principal = this.principal.dividedBy(numberOfPrincipalPaymentPeriods, mc);
+        this.fixedPrincipalAmount = principal.getAmount();
+    }
+    // ...
+    return principal;
+}
+```
+
+**选择逻辑**：[LoanApplicationTerms.calculateTotalPrincipalForPeriod()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L974-L1002)
+```java
+case DECLINING_BALANCE:
+    switch (this.amortizationMethod) {
+        case EQUAL_INSTALLMENTS:
+            // → 等额本息：PMT - 当期利息
+        case EQUAL_PRINCIPAL:
+            // → 等额本金：固定本金
+    }
+```
+
+### 2.3 利息计算基准（Days In Year / Days In Month）
+
+Fineract 支持多种日计数基准，通过两个枚举类配置：
+
+#### 配置枚举类
+
+| 枚举 | 位置 | 可选值 |
+|------|------|--------|
+| [DaysInYearType](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInYearType.java) | `fineract-core/.../DaysInYearType.java` | `ACTUAL(1)`, `DAYS_360(360)`, `DAYS_364(364)`, `DAYS_365(365)` |
+| [DaysInMonthType](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInMonthType.java) | `fineract-core/.../DaysInMonthType.java` | `ACTUAL(1)`, `DAYS_30(30)` |
+
+#### 周期利率计算逻辑
+
+周期利率的计算位于 [LoanApplicationTerms.periodicInterestRate()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1399-L1488)：
+
+```java
+private BigDecimal periodicInterestRate(...) {
+    // 1. 计算一年内的期数
+    final long loanTermPeriodsInOneYear = calculatePeriodsInOneYear(calculator);
+    
+    // 2. 日利率 = 年利率 / 一年天数（根据 DaysInYearType）
+    final BigDecimal oneDayOfYearInterestRate = this.annualNominalInterestRate
+            .divide(loanTermPeriodsInYearBigDecimal, mc)
+            .divide(divisor, mc);
+    
+    // 3. 周期利率 = 日利率 × 周期天数
+    //    周期天数根据 DaysInMonthType 计算（ACTUAL=实际天数, 30=固定30天）
+    switch (this.repaymentPeriodFrequencyType) {
+        case MONTHS:
+            if (daysInMonthType.isDaysInMonth_30()) {
+                numberOfDaysInPeriod = BigDecimal.valueOf(30 * this.repaymentEvery);
+            } else {
+                numberOfDaysInPeriod = BigDecimal.valueOf(getExactDaysInPeriod(periodStartDate, periodEndDate));
+            }
+    }
+    
+    return oneDayOfYearInterestRate.multiply(numberOfDaysInPeriod, mc);
+}
+```
+
+#### 一年期数计算
+
+[LoanApplicationTerms.calculatePeriodsInOneYear()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1496-L1521)：
+- 当 `DaysInYearType != ACTUAL` 时，直接使用配置值（360/364/365）
+- 当 `DaysInYearType == ACTUAL` 且非 PMT 计算时，使用当年实际天数（闰年 366）
+
+#### Leap Year 策略
+
+[DaysInYearCustomStrategyType](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInYearCustomStrategyType.java) 定义了两种闰年策略：
+- `FULL_LEAP_YEAR`：闰年始终按 366 天计算
+- `FEB_29_PERIOD_ONLY`：仅当计息区间包含 2 月 29 日时才按 366 天
+
+#### 相关计算类
+
+| 类 | 位置 | 职责 |
+|----|------|------|
+| [DefaultPaymentPeriodsInOneYearCalculator](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/DefaultPaymentPeriodsInOneYearCalculator.java) | fineract-loan | 计算一年期数及还款周期分数 |
+| [AprCalculator](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/AprCalculator.java) | fineract-loan | APR 年化利率计算 |
